-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                            INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This document contains instructions for installing and configuring Harmony.

Our source files (www.github/...) include clang (v. Dragonegg 3.0) and 
LLVM (v. 3.0), so you do not need to download these tools separately. You
should make sure, however, that you have the following system prerequisites:

1) 32 or 64 bit Unix O/S.
2) Updated linker ....
3) ? 

